sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS Reencrypt
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant API as DS Pipeline API Server<br/>8888/TCP REST<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant MariaDB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant MinIO as MinIO / S3<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant Pods as Pipeline Pods
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 1: Pipeline Run Execution

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v1beta1/runs<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Route->>OAuth: Forward (Reencrypt TLS)<br/>8443/TCP
    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate OpenShift OAuth token
    OAuth->>API: Forward (proxied identity)<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS (PodToPodTLS)

    API->>MariaDB: Store run metadata<br/>3306/TCP MySQL<br/>Optional TLS (service-ca)<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    MariaDB-->>API: OK

    API->>MinIO: Store compiled pipeline<br/>9000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Optional TLS<br/>Auth: Access Key/Secret Key
    MinIO-->>API: OK

    API->>K8sAPI: Create Workflow CR<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>API: Workflow created

    K8sAPI->>Argo: Watch event: new Workflow<br/>HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Argo->>K8sAPI: Create Pipeline Pod<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI->>Pods: Pod scheduled & started

    Pods->>MLMD: Record execution metadata<br/>8080/TCP gRPC<br/>Optional TLS (PodToPodTLS)<br/>Auth: NetworkPolicy-restricted
    MLMD->>MariaDB: Store ML metadata<br/>3306/TCP MySQL

    PA->>API: Sync workflow status<br/>8888/TCP REST + 8887/TCP gRPC<br/>Optional TLS (PodToPodTLS)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token<br/>(audience: pipelines.kubeflow.org)

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 2: DSPA Reconciliation

    participant DSPO as DSPO Controller<br/>Operator Namespace

    K8sAPI->>DSPO: Watch event: DSPA CR change<br/>HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    DSPO->>MariaDB: Health check connection<br/>3306/TCP MySQL<br/>Optional TLS<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    MariaDB-->>DSPO: Connection OK

    DSPO->>MinIO: Health check connection<br/>9000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Optional TLS<br/>Auth: Access Key/Secret Key
    MinIO-->>DSPO: Connection OK

    DSPO->>K8sAPI: Apply component manifests<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>DSPO: Resources applied

    Note over DSPO: Deploy order: DB + Storage -> Common -><br/>API Server -> Persistence Agent -><br/>Scheduled Workflow -> UI -><br/>Workflow Controller -> MLMD
